@push_leverage_positions
title: Push for more positions
view-if: parlament_coalition_leverage < 10
choose-if: parlament_coalition_push < left_tripartite_coalition_phase and left_tripartite_coalition_phase < 3
unavailable-subtitle: We've already pushed for more demands. [? if left_tripartite_coalition_phase < 3: We'll have to wait for the next round of negotiations to try again. ?]
on-arrival: {!
    if (Q.left_tripartite_coalition_phase == 1) {
        Q[Q.parlament_current_icv + "_relations"] -= 5;
        Q.psc_relations -= 5;
    } else {
        Q[Q.parlament_current_icv + "_relations"] -= 3;
        Q.psc_relations -= 3;
    }
    Q.parlament_coalition_leverage += 4;
    Q.parlament_coalition_push += 1;
!}
go-to: changes

@send_back
title: Send this [? if left_tripartite_coalition_phase > 1: counter-?]proposal
view-if: parlament_coalition_changes
subtitle: [?if parlament_coalition_push >= left_tripartite_coalition_phase: Back-and-forth negotiations will take some time, but may give us the extra edge needed for a better deal. ?]
on-arrival: {!
    Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_accept = true;
    if (Q.parlament_coalition_push >= Q.left_tripartite_coalition_phase) {
        Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_accept = false;
    } else {
        if (Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_vp == "erc" && Q.left_tripartite_coalition_phase != 3) {
            Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_accept = false;
        }
        if ((Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_interior || Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_education) && Q.left_tripartite_coalition_phase < 2) {
            Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_accept = false;
        }
    }
!}
go-to: decision

@decision
title: decision
go-to: accept if parlament_coalition_proposal_accept; next_phase if parlament_coalition_proposal_accept = false

@next_phase
title: next phase
go-to: new_elections if left_tripartite_coalition_phase >= 3; new_phase_2 if not left_tripartite_coalition_phase >= 3

@new_phase_2
on-arrival: {!
    Q.parlament_coalition_changes = false;
    Q.left_tripartite_coalition_phase += 1;
    Q.month_actions += 1;
    Q.independence_trust -= 2;
    Q.social_dissent += 5;

    if (Q.parlament_current_icv_s > Q.psc_parlament_s) {
        Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_vp = Q.parlament_current_icv;
    } else {
        Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_vp = "psc";
    }
    Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_interior = "erc";
    Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_economy = "erc";
    Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_foreign = "erc";
    Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_health = "erc";
    Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_education = "erc";
    Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_territory = "erc";
    Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_bnl = "erc";

    var psc_leverage = (Q.psc_parlament_s / Q.parlament_coalition_erc_psc_icv_s)*55 + 12 - 3*Q.left_tripartite_coalition_phase;
    var icv_leverage = (Q.parlament_current_icv_s / Q.parlament_coalition_erc_psc_icv_s)*55 + 12 - 3*Q.left_tripartite_coalition_phase;

    // the partner holding the Speaker has spent capital there, so less pull on ministries
    if (Q.speaker_party == "psc") psc_leverage -= 10;
    if (Q.speaker_party == Q.parlament_current_icv) icv_leverage -= 10;

    if (icv_leverage > 10) {
        Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_education = Q.parlament_current_icv;
        icv_leverage -= 7;
    }
    if (icv_leverage > 5) {
        Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_territory = Q.parlament_current_icv;
        icv_leverage -= 5;
    }
    if (psc_leverage > 10) {
        Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_interior = "psc";
        psc_leverage -= 10;
    }
    if (psc_leverage > 10) {
        Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_economy = "psc";
        psc_leverage -= 10;
    } else if (psc_leverage > 7) {
        Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_health = "psc";
        psc_leverage -= 7;
    }

    if (psc_leverage >= icv_leverage && psc_leverage > 5) {
        Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_bnl = "psc";
    } else if (icv_leverage > 5) {
        Q.parlament_coalition_proposal_bnl = Q.parlament_current_icv;
    }
!} 

The PSC's and [+ parlament_current_icv +]'s representatives were initially dubious about our new proposal. [? if parlament_coalition_proposal_vp = "erc": They were very skeptical about us taking the Vice-Presidency. ?][? if parlament_coalition_proposal_interior = "erc" or parlament_coalition_proposal_education = "erc": Some eyebrows were [? if parlament_coalition_proposal_vp = "erc": also ?]risen when we demanded [? if parlament_coalition_proposal_education = "erc": Education?] [? if parlament_coalition_proposal_education = "erc" and parlament_coalition_proposal_interior = "erc": and ?][? if parlament_coalition_proposal_interior = "erc": Interior?].?] We will have to wait until the PSC, [+ parlament_current_icv +], and ERC negotiating teams reconvene to advance negotiations.

- @post_event: And so, time passes...


@accept
title: Accept proposal
view-if: not parlament_coalition_changes and left_tripartite_coalition_phase > 1
choose-if: not parlament_coalition_changes
unavailable-subtitle: We have proposed changes, which will require approval by both the PSC and [+ parlament_current_icv +].
on-arrival: {!
    Q.left_tripartite_coalition_phase = 0;
    Q.cat_coalition_disp = `<span style="color: var(--erc); font-style: italic;">Left</span> <span style="color: [? if parlament_current_icv = 'icv': var(--icv)?][? if parlament_current_icv = 'csqp': var(--csqp)?][? if parlament_current_icv = 'cecp': var(--cecp)?][? if parlament_current_icv = 'ecp': var(--ecp)?]; font-style: italic;">Tri</span><span style='color: var(--psc); font-style: italic;'>partite</span>`;
    Q.erc_in_gob = true;
    Q.erc_supporting = true;
    Q.cat_coalition = ["psc", "erc", Q.parlament_current_icv];
    Q.cat_coalition_dissent = 0;

    Q.position_disp = "Generalitat";

    Q.cup_in_gob = false;
    Q.cup_supporting = false;
    Q.independence_trust -= 10;
!}

After some ardous negotiations, we have finally reached an agreement with the PSC and [+ parlament_current_icv +] to form a [+ cat_coalition_disp +]. Let's hope cooperation continues during this legislature, and that promises are kept!


- @parlament_coalition_resolve: A new government is formed


@new_elections
title: new elections
on-arrival: {!
    Q.left_tripartite_coalition_phase = 0;
    Q[Q.parlament_current_icv + "_relations"] -= 5;
    Q.psc_relations -= 5;
    Q.social_dissent += 10;
    Q.snap_blame = Q.player_party;
    Q.snap_counterparty = "psc";
    Q.snap_severity = 0.12;
!}
call: snap_election

After three rounds of negotiations, we've reached the end of the road. With no agreement in sight and no more time for back-and-forth, the only option left is to call for new elections and hope for a better result. Needless to say, neither partner are happy about this outcome.

- @post_event: We'll have to see if we fare any better this time...